&lt;tr>
&lt;td>conda create -n myenv sqlite | python=x.x&lt;/td>
&lt;td>Create an environment containing the package sqlite or python&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>conda remove -n myenv &amp;ndash;all&lt;/td>
